  "style": "",
  "texts": [
    "The participants received this task to ensure that they attended the sounds.",
    "Each functional localiser block lasted 16 seconds and each run lasted about 6.5 minutes.",
    "Data acquisitionEach session of the main experiment included a single run of the functional localiser.",
    "The thirteen participants who completed 3 sessions therefore had 3 runs of the functional localiser; the remaining two participants had 2 runs of the functional localiser.Each of the sessions consisted, in this order, of two runs of the main task, a single volume whole-head echo planar imaging (EPI) during rest, a fieldmap, and, only on the first session, a structural MRI, one more run of the main task, one run of the functional localiser, and a final run of the main task.",
    "The session order was arranged to allow participants plenty of rest between runs of the main task to minimise potential fatigue.MRI data were acquired using a Siemens Prisma 3 T (Siemens Healthineers, Erlangen, Germany) with a 64-channel head coil."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}